msgctxt "ST_Klib,Desc_AlumniumSheet.Desc_AlumniumSheet_C.mDescription"
msgid "A magnesium-rich aluminum alloy, one of the most basic parts from Aluminum."
msgstr "A magnesium-rich aluminum alloy, one of the most basic parts from Aluminum."

msgid "A metal mixture for advaned smelting. This Mixtures are used in the Foundary or in the Blast Furnace!\\r\\n\\r\\nNote: can weigh a lot. "
msgstr "A metal mixture for advaned smelting. This Mixtures are used in the Foundary or in the Blast Furnace!\\r\\n\\r\\nNote: can weigh a lot. "

msgid "A mix of Titanium Chlorides, also known 'Tickle'.\\r\\nThe purple hue stems from TiCl3.\\r\\nMainly used to produce purified Titanium."
msgstr "A mix of Titanium Chlorides, also known 'Tickle'.\\r\\nThe purple hue stems from TiCl3.\\r\\nMainly used to produce purified Titanium."

msgctxt "ST_Klib,Desc_CryoliteResidue.Desc_CryoliteResidue_C.mDescription"
msgid "A mixture of byproducts left over after refining Bauxite."
msgstr "A mixture of byproducts left over after refining Bauxite."

msgid "A network pole for transmitting and dividing information over longer distances.\\r\\n\\r\\nCan connect up to 6 cables. and attached walls."
msgstr "A network pole for transmitting and dividing information over longer distances.\\r\\n\\r\\nCan connect up to 6 cables. and attached walls."

msgid "A non-flammable, pungent-smelling gas used to refine Uranium and Titanium.\\r\\n\\r\\nOn MASSAGE-2 (AB)b, it is rarely found in underground gas wells. It can also be synthesized from Muriatic Acid."
msgstr "A non-flammable, pungent-smelling gas used to refine Uranium and Titanium.\\r\\n\\r\\nOn MASSAGE-2 (AB)b, it is rarely found in underground gas wells. It can also be synthesized from Muriatic Acid."

msgid "A plate coated with titanium metal, produced through sintering of titanium hydride made from TiCl Gas.\\r\\n\\r\\nCommonly used to coat surfaces with titanium in a process known as 'sputtering'."
msgstr "A plate coated with titanium metal, produced through sintering of titanium hydride made from TiCl Gas.\\r\\n\\r\\nCommonly used to coat surfaces with titanium in a process known as 'sputtering'."

msgid "A pre-soldered Wire, ready to be used in electronics.\\r\\nOne of the most basic parts made with Solder."
msgstr "A pre-soldered Wire, ready to be used in electronics.\\r\\nOne of the most basic parts made with Solder."

msgctxt "ST_Klib,Desc_CarbonDust.Desc_CarbonDust_C.mDescription"
msgid "A sack full of finely crushed powdered coal. Perfect for making gunpowder."
msgstr "A sack full of finely crushed powdered coal. Perfect for making gunpowder."

msgid "A semiconductor photodiode array. Converts light into electricity.\\r\\nOften used to construct Solar Panels or in advanced electronics."
msgstr "A semiconductor photodiode array. Converts light into electricity.\\r\\nOften used to construct Solar Panels or in advanced electronics."

msgctxt "ST_Klib,Desc_CateriumHeatsink.Desc_CateriumHeatsink_C.mDescription"
msgid "A small heatsink with high conductivity. Great for high power electronics."
msgstr "A small heatsink with high conductivity. Great for high power electronics."

msgid "A special KMods bonus program voucher, available through various deliveries and tasks.\\r\\nBetter hold onto this coupon - might be exchanged for rewards later on."
msgstr "A special KMods bonus program voucher, available through various deliveries and tasks.\\r\\nBetter hold onto this coupon - might be exchanged for rewards later on."

msgid "A transformative paint that can coat any kind of surface with any kind of paint finish, no matter the color or material desired.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt is so effective that FICSIT now uses it for all of their products.\\r\\n\\r\\n'Everything is just one paint coat away from becoming something new.'"
msgstr "A transformative paint that can coat any kind of surface with any kind of paint finish, no matter the color or material desired.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt is so effective that FICSIT now uses it for all of their products.\\r\\n\\r\\n'Everything is just one paint coat away from becoming something new.'"

msgid "A very special phase of Kyalite crystal with birefractive properties. It requires refinement before it can be used.\\r\\n\\r\\nNamed after D. Kerr, a visionary in the field of quantum optics."
msgstr "A very special phase of Kyalite crystal with birefractive properties. It requires refinement before it can be used.\\r\\n\\r\\nNamed after D. Kerr, a visionary in the field of quantum optics."

