msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nSome ores require higher tier mining heads.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 30 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 30 / min = 15 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."
msgstr "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nSome ores require higher tier mining heads.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 30 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 30 / min = 15 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."

msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nSome ores require higher tier mining heads.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 60 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 60 / min = 30 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."
msgstr "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nSome ores require higher tier mining heads.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 60 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 60 / min = 30 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."

msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nTough enough to mine any ore.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 120 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 120 / min = 60 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."
msgstr "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\\r\\nTough enough to mine any ore.\\r\\nStandard extraction rate: 120 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\\r\\nExample: 50% x 120 / min = 60 / min per output.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."

msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases the power required by the Modular Miner.\\r\\n\\r\\nIncreases the Miner's Mining Efficiency based on the supplied fluid. Miner will not activate unless a fluid is supplied.\\r\\n\\r\\nBonus to Mining Efficiency can be viewed from inside the Miner Menu 'Fluid Info' panel."
msgstr "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases the power required by the Modular Miner.\\r\\n\\r\\nIncreases the Miner's Mining Efficiency based on the supplied fluid. Miner will not activate unless a fluid is supplied.\\r\\n\\r\\nBonus to Mining Efficiency can be viewed from inside the Miner Menu 'Fluid Info' panel."

msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases the power required by the Modular Miner.\\r\\n\\r\\nInstantly crushes extracted ores and dirts.\\r\\n\\r\\nReduces the Mining Efficiency Bonus from Booster Modules to half their original value.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Module is not compatible with Smelter Module."
msgstr "Attached to the Modular Miner.\\r\\nIncreases the power required by the Modular Miner.\\r\\n\\r\\nInstantly crushes extracted ores and dirts.\\r\\n\\r\\nReduces the Mining Efficiency Bonus from Booster Modules to half their original value.\\r\\n\\r\\nNOTE: Module is not compatible with Smelter Module."

